==<span style="position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: 2.5px; top: -2px;">[[File:Untitled205 20240925204431.png|30px|link=]]</span> Colonies and Outposts==
'''Level 6.2''' is devoid of all other life, primarily due to [[Phenomenon 15|a certain phenomenon]] affecting the level. As it is impossible to find another wanderer within the level, forming colonies and outposts is impossible, and any reports stating such a sighting are likely the result of psychotic hallucinations caused by the level.
==<span style="position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: 2.5px; top: -2px;">[[File:Untitled205 20240925204431.png|30px|link=]]</span> Entrances and Exits==
===Entrances===
*Going through a boiler located within [[Level 5]].
*A rusted door located on [[Level 6]], which leads directly to '''Level 6.2'''.
===Exits===
*Tripping on a fallen branch leads to [[Level 6.1]]. It is worth note that intentionally doing so will not initiate the transportation.
**Additionally, entering dated metal trapdoors occasionally found on the forest floor will also lead one here. 
*Entering a hole will lead you to [[Level 8]].
*Wandering far enough will bring you to [[Level 7]].
